org.openflow.protocol

Class OFUnknownMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openflow.protocol.OFMessage
      • org.openflow.protocol.OFUnknownMessage

  • public class OFUnknownMessage
extends OFMessage
    This message is created when reading from an OpenFlow stream that delivers a message of an unknown type. This class skips over the data of the unknown message.
    Author:
    David Erickson (daviderickson@cs.stanford.edu)
